reviews.review_text:
Great Show Good Recording! Thank you!  This show is a pleasure to listen too.
Makes me think of a nice warm summer day at the beach.  Beautiful People, with sexy bathing suits dancing happy.  Show Opens with a tight and energetic Hell in A Bucket. Phil is in great form here.  You can hear the excitement of the fans through out the show that highlights with "Not Fade Away" and the fans Chant.  This was such a great party, I don't think the City of Ventura invited "The Fans and Band Back".  Great Show Good Recording!
